precis:
Amendments to the FEED GRAIN TRANSPORTATION AND STORAGE ASSISTANCE
REGULATIONS which slightly increase the subsidy rates payable on shipments
to Newfoundland in order to correct an imbalance which occurred when all
rates were reduced by 10% on April 1, 1993.
